{"tid":1526922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屬於香港人既ig challenge - 罷搭黨鐵","createTime":"2019-09-01T08:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T09:13:56.000Z","uid":9591,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a9b37dc21cbf234e179669658c743d37345ab3","tid":1526922,"uid":9591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"雖然跳閘好易，但明白好多和理非手足其實唔想犯法，但我地可以罷搭。香港有巴士小巴的士uber，邊撚個話一定要搭黨鐵？射落海我都唔撚益佢。<br />\n<br />\n但自己一個做唔夠，希望大家每次唔搭黨鐵，分享下自己由邊到去邊到(當然唔係發夢個日)，再分享下自己用左咩方法，post上story hashtag #hkwithoutmtr。<br />\n<br />\n呢種抗爭，不犯法，和平，仲可以滿足班KOL既心態，但又可以切切實實咁用金錢制裁黨鐵。唔好同我講話無辦法唔搭黨鐵，如果每日用你多少少時間係交通上面你都做唔到，衰啲講句你琴晚點鬧點喊都係無意義。<br />\n<br />\nAnyone in?"},{"pid":"a14e573b0a0914181716c19774817580bf803e35","tid":1526922,"uid":9591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a4f829ff114e158675633af9d22bfb8a0e2a3086","tid":1526922,"uid":60398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:05:32.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmZ8JRV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmZ8JRV.gif&h=d48b36ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /